  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK282">
<l>uḷḷattā luḷḷalun tītē piṟaṉporuḷaik</l>
<l>kaḷḷattāṟ kaḷvē meṉal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even the thought (of sin) is sin think not then of crafiily stealing the property of another.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
